Classes in de.tub.processor.graph that implement IProcessor
 class HierarchicalGraphProcessor

Uses of IProcessor in de.tub.processor.preprocessing
 

Classes in de.tub.processor.preprocessing that implement IProcessor
 class AbstractTextLineProcessor
          The AbstractTextLineProcessor processes lines of text with a standard delimiter of tab (i.e., '\t').
 class GpsLogLineProcessor
          This specific processor extracts the information of latitude, longitude, date and time out of text lines of a text file that has the format latitude,longitude,0,altitude,date(as #days passed since 12/30/1899),date,time.
